'desc': [u'

Chumbak Printed Men's Round Neck T-Shirt Price: Rs.350

Add this appealing blue coloured T-shirt to your wardrobe and showcase your trendy style by putting on this printed T-shirt from Chumbak. Crafted from 100 per cent cotton
column17: this ribbed round neck T-shirt provides you with maximum amount of comfort at all times. Cut for a regular fit
column18:
this casual T-shirt with half sleeves gives you a cool casual look and great fit. The attractive rubber print at the front and the back enhances your contemporary look.

Team this stylish Chumbak Round Neck Printed T-shirt with a pair of denim jeans and canvas shoes for a laidback look. Watch movies or go shopping on the weekends in this casual attire. Chumbak acquaints you with the warm and fun side of India like never before; ingenious art with a twist of mischief. Vivid prints and hues make Chumbak T-shirts both amusing and alluring.

Fabric Care

Machine wash the T-shirt inside out at 40 degree celsius and avoid wringing. Do not tumble dry and use low temperature iron.
